Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As stated in the report,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we underestimated them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! We can do it\NYou can count on us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are we going after\Nthe Abydos students again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But with what money?\NWe used up all our funds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And paying rent on this office\Ntakes up whatever we have left
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every decent company\Nneeds an office space!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I liked our tent\Nin the park from before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't care where\Nas long as I'm with the boss
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take out a loan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NBut you're on every bank's blacklist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My accounts are just frozen\Nbecause I'm a wanted criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let our\Ncommission end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky blue archive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I pedal on my bike seeking new sights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll break the monotony,\Nno longer trapped in place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daydreaming on the rooftop,\Ngazing at a sky so blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clouds like whales are always changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll embrace a past that can't be altered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharing juice in this world made of sand\Nis a taste so divine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were here alone, here without all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't laugh, I couldn't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A fateful coterie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the world's memories blow away\Nlike grains of sand one day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky, sea, wind, and you,\Nour youth will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to see why we protect what we do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this is the only place where we belong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing business\Nwith Kaiser Loans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total was 7,883,250 yen, in cash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Receipt confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, until next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe for one more month…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does Kaiser Loans\Nonly accept cash payments?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A bank transfer payment\Nwould be faster and easier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko! You can't attack\Nthat van, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start\Nthe daily meeting now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(Foreclosure Task Force\NDaily Meeting)\NSo, let's start\Nthe daily meeting now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,First, regarding the\Npart we found…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, it was traded\Non the Black Market
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of banned contraband\Nin Kivotos can be found there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as clubs unauthorized\Nby the General Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's dangerous there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68 seems\Nto frequent that market as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just like the Helmet Gangsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to take over our school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something going on\Nfor everyone to come after us like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really concerning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, investigating the connections\Nbetween these incidents
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,might be a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, It's settled then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the newest guns here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Black Market
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really packed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This place isn't controlled\Nby the General Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,yet it's unbelievably massive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we hardly ever leave Abydos,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but outside our campus,\Nthere's lots of weird places
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my first time as well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But other schools have weird stuff too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of a giant water tank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,called an aquarium
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see it one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds nice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, there's no telling\Nwhat could happen there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So please be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes\N- Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop chasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- No can do\N- We told you to come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have nothing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This uniform is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from Trinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll handle it\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All we want is that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from Trinity General School,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the richest school in all of Kivotos
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna kidnap her\Nand demand a hefty ransom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnap first, negotiate later\NIt's a good way to make money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can team up\Nif you're interested
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're willing to split the ransom money by—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ajitani Hifumi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, you said? Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's a Trinity\Nstudent doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been discontinued,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard they still\Nsell it here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or illegal guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or chemical weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Limited edition Peroro merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Peroro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This limited edition Peroro doll,\Nwith only 100 ever made
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the Momo Friends series,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Peroro so cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?\NThis old-timer doesn't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for something too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Something very hard to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but we heard it's sold here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You just came here to buy a doll,\Nbut ended up in such a mishap
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew this was\Na dangerous place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond the control\Nof the General Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so a lot of companies work\Noutside the law here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They even have their own\Nfinancial institutions and security forces
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of these organizations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,are illegal and\Nunauthorized, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we should\Navoid any security here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, you sure know a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! It's settled then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reward for saving you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,can you help us find\Nwhat we came here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-HUH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going\Nto take out a loan from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Black Market Bank, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The interest rates must be crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is if Aru even\Ngets approved for a loan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!\NOf course I'll get approved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About the parts\Nyou're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,(Taiyaki)\Nthere should be some kind of trail,\Nbut it's so hard to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like sales channels\Nor storage records…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if someone's\Ndeliberately hidden all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it seems like, at least
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliberately hidden it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the companies\Nthat dominate this market
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,don't normally do this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like,\N"Why go to such lengths?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here openly\Nengages in illegal activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's even weirder that\Nthey're hiding things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that building over there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Black Market Bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,notorious even in this place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Market Bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,According to rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly 15% of crime-related\Nfinancial assets in Kivotos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,flow through that bank
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They get money from crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,like embezzlement,\Nrobbery, and kidnapping,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and then use it to buy\Nweapons for more crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the vicious circle\Ncontinues endlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that bank is\Nfacilitating criminal activities
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, even the banks\Nare criminal organizations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Black Market Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Market Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the best security\Norganization here in the market
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are escorting that van
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A cash transport vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The bank clerk who\Ncollects our payments?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting\NHere is this month's collection
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Loans is colluding\Nwith the Black Market Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiser Loans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the loan shark company\Nrun by the notorious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Corporation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they a bad company?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Kaiser Group may be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a diversified company,\Nbut it walks a fine line between
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,legality and illegality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all take out\Na loan from Kaiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the reason\Nthey only accept cash is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so they won't leave a paper trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe our money's been\Ngoing into the Black Market Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we've been\Nfunding criminal activities!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't be sure yet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kaiser Loans has been\Ndepositing our money there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a receipt whenever\Nyou make a payment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have your evidence\Nif you find their receipt records
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But all those documents\Nmust be in their vaults already,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so we've hit a dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Market Bank has
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the strongest security system\Nin the Black Market
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other option
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What option?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that should\Ndefinitely work
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By "that" you don't mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not talking about\Nwhat I'm thinking of, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, wait\NThere has to be another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, We're only trying to\Nfind evidence of their crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't listen\Neven if I tried to stop you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hifumi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've thought ahead\Nand made you a mask too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good people!\NWe couldn't just abandon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay! I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, you can wear this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, please wait
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, A perfect fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am going with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Hifumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise\Nto help us out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How will I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ever be able to face\Nthe student council again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!\NWe're not doing anything wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If your money is being\Nused for criminal activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm\N- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Masked Swimsuit Gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you should be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I approved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We need this money ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you'll need\Nto look elsewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just one second!\NYou won't give us a loan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We even have an office\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You rent your office,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and your only\Nassets are firearms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't offer you\Na loan with just this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,bankable assets or good credit,\Nwe could offer you a loan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't you try\Ngetting a part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That really pisses me off
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to smash everything\Nand rob them blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Market Guards are here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it really is hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the guts to\Npick a fight with the Black Market
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?\NI'm so pathetic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I resolved to become\Nthe greatest outlaw
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of Kivotos
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm being stymied
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with trivial matters\Nlike a loan approval
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what I dreamed of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A hard-boiled outlaw
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,who fears nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and isn't bound by anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who I wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone drop your weapons\Nand get on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bank robbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you're told,\Nor I'll send you to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,please get on the ground,\Nso you won't get hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We told you to drop your weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to hurt\Nany ordinary citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes\N- Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, since everything's\Ngoing according to plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is it time for the next step?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Faust, give us the command
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Faust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi— No, Faust is our leader
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the boss, And I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't they…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos students?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Should we counterattack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't seem\Nto be their targets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, don't even\Nthink about resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- The delivery van that just came in…\N- I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold, cash, bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, all we want is\Nthe collection records
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh my, Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the guts to\Nrob the Black Market Bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What amazing skills\NThey're the ultimate professionals
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cool! I think I have a crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are real outlaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I'm going to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here you go\NPlease spare my life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro— I mean, Blue 2\NDid you get the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's run
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everyone, retreat\N- Adios!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No one seems to be hurt, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Block the roads and\Ncontact the Black Market Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice villainy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done on getting through\Nthe blockades, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for a\Nteacher to be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, do you\Nhave the records?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just stole all\Nthe money, Shiroko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Here are the\Ndocuments we wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be at least\Na hundred million
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Let's take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? With this, our debt…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't do that, Serika
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked so hard\Nto earn this money,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it just ended up\Nin that Black Market Bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, And if we had\Nleft this money there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it could've been used by\Ncriminals to buy more guns
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! What's wrong with\Nstealing money from bad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Serika
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dirty money,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so why can't we spend\Nit for a good cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And this amount of money\Nwill really help with our debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino will say no regardless
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Shiroko\NYou know me too well
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We only need the documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not the money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we justify stealing\Nfrom criminals now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,what about the next time?\NAnd after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If this becomes a habit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're in another tough spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we might become the criminals,\Nand say it was inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As an old-timer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you cute\Nyoungins do that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we end up resorting to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd have been better
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to use Nonomi's glorious\Ngold card from the get-go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hoshino, you said no to…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to pay off\Nour debt the right way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or we won't be Abydos\NHigh School anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go back with\Njust the documents we need
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you all say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exactly know\Nyour circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but money like this will\Nonly bring you more trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a cursed item
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry\NI'm not your enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why is she here?\N- Should we shoot her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't shoot her\Nwhen she means no harm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just a little
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you guys at the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Robbing and retreating\Nso efficiently…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to meet\Nsuch amazing outlaws
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was totally shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I really admire how\Nbold you all were
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my absolute best
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to not be bound\Nby laws or rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and become a truly free spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of outlaw I want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,can you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean the name\Nof your organization or team
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to always remember\Nyour wonderful deeds today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nonomi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People call us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the Masked Swimsuit Gang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Masked Swimsuit Gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cool and chic name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye,\Na tooth for a tooth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Forsake mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and walk the path of chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our motto
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Coool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Let's go back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Adios, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're riding off into the sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun hasn't set yet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Walk the path of chaos,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll engrave those words on my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When should we tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be funnier to tell her later
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they leave that behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean we won't\Nhave to skip meals anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Walk the path of chaos,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru's been talking nonstop\Nabout the Masked Swimsuit Gang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When will she realize the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss,\Nabout that Masked Swimsuit Gang…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the Abydos students
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru is totally shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the window seat,\NI'm seeking where my heart belongs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So that sadness won't take over me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgetting time without knowing why
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We laughed together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just an ordinary sight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing they won't come true once more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could stay strong and beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the moon in the midday sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I be able to forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The mistakes and regrets of that day,\Nall willingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The important things are always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What we realize only after they've passed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Reaching out towards the moon\Nin the midday sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can't reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, unforgettable beautiful days
